  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/5932155c22890d1b204e3dadbfe91472.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=164 /></span><br><br>Re-enlist with Toy Soldiers HD and experience the award-winning XBLA hit updated for a whole new generation!  <br><br>Command from above or take direct control below. Lead your  foot soldiers, cavalry, tanks and planes to victory. Deploy an exciting arsenal of guns, gas, howitzers, mortars, troops, flamethrowers and vehicles to protect your Toybox in vintage WWI toy dioramas.<br><br>Toy Soldiers is a multi-genre action-strategy game in which players command antique WWI toy soldiers vying for control of the trench-filled diorama battlefields of Europe. The original classic has been overhauled and upgraded with new content, skins, gameplay, expanded game modes, improved controls and graphical upgrades. We’ve also included all  the original DLC and a few new levels as well!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/acd43abb6cf564b4fb02ed489643c25d.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=165 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Amazing Shell-Cam</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/b4a9845bed35e177c60a01b868dfe53f.poster.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/b4a9845bed35e177c60a01b868dfe53f.webm?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/b4a9845bed35e177c60a01b868dfe53f.mp4?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take a ride and follow your shot right onto its target!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Man the Guns</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/ec095bb68f8fab076df94f6526acba61.poster.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/ec095bb68f8fab076df94f6526acba61.webm?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/ec095bb68f8fab076df94f6526acba61.mp4?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Leap into your strategically placed units and take hands-on control.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fierce Boss Battles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/c54b8ec7a3624f2aea71d3df49c29163.poster.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/c54b8ec7a3624f2aea71d3df49c29163.webm?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/c54b8ec7a3624f2aea71d3df49c29163.mp4?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Remember: this is a war of attrition, do whatever it takes against huge enemy bosses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Commandeer Machines of War</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/229c33f6d4be0f940e5d9ac5d181589c.poster.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/229c33f6d4be0f940e5d9ac5d181589c.webm?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/229c33f6d4be0f940e5d9ac5d181589c.mp4?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Think you can drive it better? Jump behind the wheel and drive (or fly) these classic machines of war yourself.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Miniaturized Mayhem</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/de270c28c56c19b31e82f9f37e446d9d.poster.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/de270c28c56c19b31e82f9f37e446d9d.webm?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/de270c28c56c19b31e82f9f37e446d9d.mp4?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Intense battlefield action as these miniature models unleash mayhem on each other!",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/5932155c22890d1b204e3dadbfe91472.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=164 /></span><br><br>Re-enlist with Toy Soldiers HD and experience the award-winning XBLA hit updated for a whole new generation!  <br><br>Command from above or take direct control below. Lead your  foot soldiers, cavalry, tanks and planes to victory. Deploy an exciting arsenal of guns, gas, howitzers, mortars, troops, flamethrowers and vehicles to protect your Toybox in vintage WWI toy dioramas.<br><br>Toy Soldiers is a multi-genre action-strategy game in which players command antique WWI toy soldiers vying for control of the trench-filled diorama battlefields of Europe. The original classic has been overhauled and upgraded with new content, skins, gameplay, expanded game modes, improved controls and graphical upgrades. We’ve also included all  the original DLC and a few new levels as well!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/acd43abb6cf564b4fb02ed489643c25d.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=165 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Amazing Shell-Cam</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/b4a9845bed35e177c60a01b868dfe53f.poster.avif?t=1666185853\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/b4a9845bed35e177c60a01b868dfe53f.webm?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446160/extras/b4a9845bed35e177c60a01b868dfe53f.mp4?t=1666185853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take a ride and follow your shot right onto its target!<h2 class=\"